The paper deals with updating nonmonotonic knowledge bases represented as logic programs, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses postulates for update and revision operators, which are relevant to databases (cs.DB) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also considers computational complexity, which is a topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC).
